      <layout-options>
        <caption>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>Decline in fishing activity during the summer known as &quot;Summer doldrums&quot; due to a combination of high water temperatures, reduced oxygen levels, and the aftermath of the spring spawning season.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </caption>
      </layout-options>
      <table>
        <view>
          <datasources>
            <datasource caption='fleet_monthly (fleet_data)' name='federated.08o8pcx0edzbjh1cnwrze1bvnlik' />
